OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with some rain,
OL,6,Fmainly in the north. Then still a few
OL,7,Fshowers this afternoon but some hazy
OL,8,Fsunshine breaking through. Brisk
OL,9,Fwesterly winds. Quite warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be cloudy
OL,12,Fwith a few outbreaks of rain. Then the
OL,13,Frest of the night will be cloudy but
OL,14,Fbecoming largely dry. Winds easing.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FChance of some patchy rain at
OL,17,Ffirst otherwise dry and rather cloudy,
OL,18,Fsome afternoon hazy sunshine in the
OL,19,Feast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
